                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant B</hi> 11.) On Saturday night, about twelve o'clock, I was in Horseferry-road—I saw the prisoner take a breast of mutton off the prosecutor's show-board, and run away with it—I caught him in my arms, and took him back with it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You were close to him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About twenty yards off—I never lost sight of him—he was quite sober.</p>
